-- Venezuela says takes over local Stanford Bank
-- 
-- Thu Feb 19, 2009 7:22am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/02/19/us-stanford-venezuela-bank-sb-idUSTRE51I2H420090219

 

 CARACAS  (Reuters) - Venezuela has taken control of a local bank owned by Allen Stanford, who faces U.S. fraud charges, Venezuela's finance minister said on Thursday. 

 (Reporting by Ana Isabel Martinez and Deisy Buitrago, Writing by Brian Ellsworth, Editing by Sandra Maler)